ZH: 我并不否定你的观点。
EN: I don't deny your point of view.

ZH: 他常常否定别人的建议。
EN: He often negates other people's suggestions.

ZH: 她坚决否定了这个谣言。
EN: She strongly denied the rumor.

ZH: 你不能否定事实。
EN: You cannot deny the fact.

ZH: 他不愿意否定他在错误中的角色。
EN: He is reluctant to deny his role in the mistake.

ZH: 她对自己的错误行为始终保持否定的态度。
EN: She maintains a denial attitude towards her wrong behavior.

ZH: 他在报告中否定了所有的指责。
EN: He refuted all the accusations in the report.

ZH: 这篇文章否定了传统观点。
EN: This article challenges traditional views.

ZH: 他总是以否定的方式回答问题。
EN: He always responds to questions in a negative way.

ZH: 这部电影可能会否定你对现实的看法。
EN: This movie might challenge your perception of reality.

ZH: 他否定了自己参与事件的可能性。
EN: He denied the possibility of his involvement in the event.

ZH: 这个政策受到了广泛的否定。
EN: This policy has been widely criticized.

ZH: 她否定了她在迟到事件中的责任。
EN: She denied responsibility for the lateness.

ZH: 一些人对这个理论持否定态度。
EN: Some people have a negative attitude towards this theory.

ZH: 这个研究结果直接否定了之前的假设。
EN: The research findings directly contradict the previous hypothesis.

ZH: 他坚持否定全球变暖的现象。
EN: He persists in denying the phenomenon of global warming.

ZH: 他的拒绝否定了我们的请求。
EN: His refusal denies our request.

ZH: 孩子们很难接受父母对他们的否定。
EN: Children find it hard to accept their parents' negation.

ZH: 这个论点已被证明是错误的，无法否定。
EN: The argument has been proven wrong and cannot be negated.

ZH: 家人和朋友的赞美能否定一些内在的不安全感。
EN: Praise from family and friends can negate some inner insecurities.

ZH: 施行这个政策将会导致一些不可否定的影响。
EN: Implementing this policy will lead to some undeniable consequences.
